file.name: ValueGeneration.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: 'test'
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /content:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: 'test'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - rangedInteger
                  - rangedFloat
                  - enum
                  - date
                  - dateTime
                  - uuid
                  - email
                  - uri
                  - hostname
                  - ipv4
                  - ipv6
                  - byte
                  - shortString
                  - longString
                  - array
                  - uniqueArrayOfObjects
                  - freeForm
                  - writeOnlyBoolean
                  - writeOnlyInteger
                  - writeOnlyNumber
                  - writeOnlyString
                  - writeOnlyArray
                  - writeOnlyObject
                properties:
                  rangedInteger:
                    type: integer
                    minimum: 1
                    maximum: 5
                  rangedFloat:
                    type: number
                    minimum: 1.0
                    maximum: 1.5
                    multipleOf: 0.1
                  enum:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - enumValue1
                      - enumValue2
                      - enumValue3
                  date:
                    type: string
                    format: date
                  dateTime:
                    type: string
                    format: 'date-time'
                  uuid:
                    type: string
                    format: uuid
                  email:
                    type: string
                    format: email
                  uri:
                    type: string
                    format: uri
                  hostname:
                    type: string
                    format: hostname
                  ipv4:
                    type: string
                    format: ipv4
                  ipv6:
                    type: string
                    format: ipv6
                  byte:
                    type: string
                    format: byte
                  html:
                    type: string
                    format: html
                  shortString:
                    type: string
                    minLength: 2
                    maxLength: 4
                  longString:
                    type: string
                    minLength: 100
                    maxLength: 105
                  array:
                    type: array
                    minItems: 5
                    maxItems: 5
                    items:
                      type: integer
                  uniqueArrayOfObjects:
                    type: array
                    uniqueItems: true
                    minItems: 1
                    maxItems: 5
                    items:
                      type: object
                      required:
                        - key
                      properties:
                        key:
                          type: string
                          enum:
                            - value
                  freeForm:
                    type: object
                    minProperties: 1
                    maxProperties: 1
                    additionalProperties: { }
                  freeFormWithBooleanOption:
                    type: object
                    minProperties: 1
                    maxProperties: 1
                    additionalProperties: true
                  hashMap:
                    type: object
                    minProperties: 1
                    maxProperties: 1
                    additionalProperties:
                      type: string
                  fixedHashMap:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                      default:
                        type: string
                        enum:
                          - value
                    required:
                      - default
                    minProperties: 1
                    maxProperties: 1
                    additionalProperties:
                      type: string
                      enum:
                        - value
                  writeOnlyBoolean:
                    type: boolean
                    writeOnly: true
                  writeOnlyInteger:
                    type: integer
                    writeOnly: true
                  writeOnlyNumber:
                    type: number
                    writeOnly: true
                  writeOnlyString:
                    type: string
                    writeOnly: true
                  writeOnlyArray:
                    type: array
                    writeOnly: true
                    items:
                      type: string
                  writeOnlyObject:
                    type: object
                    writeOnly: true
                    additionalProperties: true
